  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "Rinse the quinoa and cook it according to package instructions.",
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Sauté the onion and garlic until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the roasted rice, cumin powder, paprika powder, and salt. Stir well to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, stirring frequently.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a large bowl and let it cool slightly.",
    "Add the cooked quinoa to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to individual dolsot stone bowls.",
    "Bake the bowls in the preheated oven for 10-12 minutes, or until the quinoa is lightly toasted and the rice is crispy.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and Greek yogurt (if using)."
